## Timeline  

- **1990s (20th Century):** Earned her B.A. from Grambling State University.  
- **2000 (21st Century):** Earned her Ph.D. in African American Literature from Howard University.  
- **2014 (21st Century):** Appointed Chair of the Department of English at Howard University.  
- **2021 (21st Century):** Became Dean of the Graduate School at Howard University.  
- **Present:** Continues to lead academic initiatives and contribute to Africana literary scholarship.  

